    <div class="alpheios-lex-entry" lemma-id="n6115" body-key="α">
          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">μέσος, μέσσος</span></b> : <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">in the
            middle of;</span>
          <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">μέσσῃ ἁλί</span>, <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">in mid-sea</span>,
            <i><span class="en">Od. 4.844</span></i>
          <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">; ἥμενοι ἐν μέσσοισι</span>, ‘in the midst of
          them,’ <i><span class="en">Od. 4.281</span></i>; of time, <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">μέσον ἦμαρ</span>; as subst., <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">μέσον</span>, <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">the middle;</span>
          <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἐς μέσον τιθέναι</span>, ‘offer for
          competition,’ as prize, <i><span class="en">Il. 23.794</span></i>
          <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">; ἐς μέσον ἀμφοτέροις δικάζειν</span>,
          ‘impartially,’ <i><span class="en">Il. 23.574</span></i>; as adv.,
            <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">μέσον</span>, <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">in the middle</span>,
            <i><span class="en">Il. 12.167</span></i>, <i><span class="en">Od. 14.300</span></i>.</div> <div class="alpheios-lex-footnotes en"> </div>
